<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太棒了！<delay frames="30" />
烟花一个接一个地绽放吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要打起精神好好享受啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看！<delay8 />是烟花！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这规模好大啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />一起兴奋起来吧！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开始了、开始了！！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花大会终于开始了！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要竭尽全力地享受啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“嘭”的一声，烟花绽放在空中，<delay20 />
看着这场景你是不是也很兴奋？！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很好！<delay8 />一起嗨起来吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />闻着烟花的气味，<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就会让人觉得，<delay8 />
原来今年，<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也到这个时节了啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿，<delay8 />你说……<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />升空烟花从侧面看，
会是什么样子的啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你<delay8 />知道吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />刚才的烟花好大啊？！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超级亮，<delay20 />有一瞬间我还以为
是太阳出来了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">烟花升空时的声音，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总让我想到起跑时<delay20 />
发令枪的声音！<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为<delay8 />不知道何时会响，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人觉得很紧张呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有尽力享受烟花的乐趣吗？！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可是直到最后一刻，<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都保持情绪高涨的哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不要因为<delay8 />烟花快放完了，<delay20 />
就松懈下来哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种一般都是，<delay20 />
越临近结束<delay8 />越精彩的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 06 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><10_14 arg="0" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="150" />烟花——！！<size value="100" /><delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="150" />放烟花喽——！！！<size value="100" /><size value="100" /><delay40 /><size value="100" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_9 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在干什么啊，<tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />靠大喊来锻炼腹肌，<delay20 />
现在就是最好的机会！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>